      // SECTION 2
      .s2-wrapper
        section.section2(style='')
          h1.section2__header WHAT IS BINARY OPTIONS?
          h5.section2__subheader A binary option is a forecast to raise or lower the value of an exchange asset
          //- img.section2__img(src='assets/img/s2.jpg' alt='s2.jpg')
          .highstock-container#highstock-container(style='width: 100%; height: 300px')

          .section2__instruction-container
            .section2__instruction-item.wow.bounceInLeft(data-wow-delay="0.6s" data-wow-offset='100')
              h5.section2__instruction-header
                i.fas.fa-crosshairs
                //= ' '
                | 1. Select asset
              p.section2__instruction-body Select an asset, such as currency, commodity or stock
            .section2__instruction-item.wow.bounceInLeft(data-wow-delay="0.3s" data-wow-offset='100')
              h5.section2__instruction-header
                i.fas.fa-chart-line
                //= ' '
                | 2. Make a prediction
              p.section2__instruction-body Make a forecast to decrease or increase the value of an asset
            .section2__instruction-item.wow.bounceInLeft(data-wow-offset='100')
              h5.section2__instruction-header
                i.far.fa-money-bill-alt
                //= ' '
                | 3. Make a profit
              p.section2__instruction-body Make a profit! If your forecast was justified - you get a pre-specified win amount
      // /SECTION 2

      // SECTION 3
      .s3-wrapper
        section.section3
          p For profit, there is no need to buy the asset itself. You just enter into a deal to make a correct forecast, the price will rise or fall. The size of the price change is not necessary to determine - just the direction.
      // /SECTION 3

      // SECTION 4
      .s4-wrapper
        img.section4__bg(src='assets/img/graphic-1.png' alt='graphic-1.png')
        section.section4
          h1.section4__header OUR ADVANTAGES

          .section4__buttons-holder
            a.page-btn.section4__btn.section4__btn_activ(data-choice="security") SECURITY
            a.page-btn.section4__btn(data-choice="clients") CUSTOMER SUPPORT
            a.page-btn.section4__btn(data-choice="trade") KINDS OF TRADE

          .section4__cards-holder
            .section4__card.wow.fadeIn(data-choice="security" data-wow-offset='100')
              i.far.fa-credit-card
              h5.section4__card-header PAYMENTS (DEPOSITS)
              .section4__card-body Support for payment card types (VISA, MasterCard, Maestro) in accordance with the requirements of PCI DSS. Bank transfers and support of BTC crypto currencies.
            .section4__card.wow.fadeIn(data-choice="security" data-wow-delay="0.3s" data-wow-offset='100')
              i.fas.fa-wrench
              h5.section4__card-header REGULATORY
              .section4__card-body PlatinumTrade is an adjustable SVG broker, we guarantee safe and reliable trading for every trader.
            .section4__card.wow.fadeIn(data-choice="security" data-wow-delay="0.6s" data-wow-offset='100')
              i.fas.fa-shield-alt
              h5.section4__card-header PUNISHED TRADE
              .section4__card-body Open an account and get one risk-free transaction for a successful start on the way to financial success—é
            .section4__card(data-choice="clients")
              i.far.fa-clock
              h5.section4__card-header SUPPORT SERVICE
              .section4__card-body We work in 12/5 mode. PlatinumTrade has a highly professional customer support service.
            .section4__card(data-choice="clients")
              i.fas.fa-link
              h5.section4__card-header COMMUNICATION
              .section4__card-body Contact us right now, in a convenient way for you in the CONTACTS section.
            .section4__card(data-choice="clients")
              i.far.fa-question-circle
              h5.section4__card-header FAQ
              .section4__card-body Training in trading and working with the platform - will quickly help the beginner learn trading.
            .section4__card(data-choice="trade")
              i.far.fa-thumbs-up
              h5.section4__card-header INDEPENDENT TRADE
              .section4__card-body Independent trading allows you to fully concentrate on trading on the market, on your reactions and relieves of the need to worry for the trading group if it cooperates with that.
            .section4__card(data-choice="trade")
              i.fas.fa-retweet
              h5.section4__card-header AUTOMATIC TRADE
              .section4__card-body Automatic advisers work on algorithms that are created on the basis of knowledge and experience of traders from around the world. Thus, you can at any time use ready-made working schemes that do not have to learn for a long time.
            .section4__card(data-choice="trade")
              i.far.fa-handshake
              h5.section4__card-header TRUST MANAGEMENT
              .section4__card-body Trust management selects many people who want to simply invest the available funds and not engage in trading activities. A professional manager with experience in trading in financial markets will multiply your funds.
      // /SECTION 4

